        {
            "_id": "5qo8PwcNs0JaqVRw",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
            "name": "Statue",
            "sort": 900000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Until the next time she acts, the stone sister appears to be a statue. She has an automatic result of 34 on Deception checks and DCs to pass as a statue. Since the Field of Maidens is filled with thousands of statues just like her, most of which aren't stone sisters, it's incredibly difficult to recognize her true nature.</p>"
                },
